:0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:00:52.000Z","msg":"香港應該可以起艦隊..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:05:31.000Z","msg":"英鎊"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:07:14.000Z","msg":"30億鎊都係3百億港紙<br />\n一個艦隊又唔駛廿隻航母<br />\n而家講緊10000億填海"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:08:57.000Z","msg":"香港買航母要300,000 億諮詢費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2ed4f9c7475e7077e7ea9c4b2aad75b2786397","tid":1168922,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4fa2152779ebcc9f940b79f34e425e54e947339","tid":1168922,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:33:21.000Z","msg":"強國海軍<br />\n紀律嚴明<br />\n<br />\n唔似某「強」國海軍<br />\n起再多船都無用"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:09:14.000Z","msg":"用直升機載雞去食野味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0df12fd45c078a2054e378a56f114442f17d3f","tid":1168922,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:09:41.000Z","msg":"上校艦長咁就玩完<br />\n明明應該做完艦長就升白廳又或者升准將"}]}